Dutch

English
A couple on a holiday in the Caribbean decide to spend the day on a scuba
diving trip. But was it the wrong decision? When a mis-count happens on the
boat, Susan and Daniel are left behind in the middle of the ocean, the boat
long gone. With all their hopes set on the boat coming back to rescue them,
they try to keep themselves safe, especially when sharks start to appear.
